CAE Industries Ltd sey dia link flight simulator, dem award am contract by U.S. Army for two helicopter simulator, wey di company dey valued at di same price as 37 million Canadian dollars (US$31.5 million).

Cain talk sey di first ah-64 Apache war mission simulator na C$19 million.

Dem dey plan to discharge am for late 1991.

Di second simulator cost between C$16.4 million and C$18 million, CAE yarn sey depending on di soldier choice.

Oga na one man from Toronto wey be sey na im dey do commercial, military simulator, and training equipment.

